data.value: We have over 30 years of experience owning, repairing, maintaining and operating all types of Rover P6 cars, 2000, 2200 and 3500, saloon and estate Our current fleet includes everyday users 1966 Rover 2000, and 1972 Rover 2000TC Export, 1975 Rover 2200 Auto, 1972 Rover 3500 . Joined more classic car clubs that are mostly committee level and now we have turned our expert knowledge and experience into our Rover P6 parts business 'MGBD Parts'
